data.description: Welcome to this charming cottage nestled in the heart of the highly desired community of Lake Forest in Daphne. Recently renovated entirely on the interior as well as a new roof and HVAC in 2022, this cozy home offers a delightful blend of modern comforts and southern charm. The cottage features a wooded back yard, perfect for enjoying the beauty of nature right at your doorstep. Step outside and be greeted by a new screen porch, where you can relax and unwind with your favorite book or enjoy the company of loved ones.  The interior boasts tasteful updates that enhance both functionality and style. With its inviting atmosphere and thoughtful design, this cottage is an ideal retreat from the hustle and bustle of everyday life. Whether you're looking for a rental property investment or for primary residence, this home provides all the amenities you need.  Located within a community rich in amenities, there's no shortage of things to do nearby. From swimming pools to playgrounds to walking trails, residents have access to an array of recreational options just steps away from their front door.  Don't miss out on the opportunity to experience southern living at its finest. Schedule your showing today and make this charming cottage your own slice of paradise in Alabama! Buyer and/or buyers agent to verify all information deemed reliable.
